snippet.title: Wario World gameplay pt. 1
snippet.description: After playing Wario Land: Shake It! last night, I was on the lvl Glittertown, and the music there was a remix of the second lvl in Wario World. So then after I beat it I decided to make a Wario World video of me playing on one of my favorite lvls, Wonky Circus. There r three parts. Comment, rate, and enjoy!
